Three Type of error we must handler
1. Undhandled Promise rejection error
2. Uncaught Exception
3. MongoDB Error -- Also called CastError -- error (Done in middleware folder)

Other Error For Safety Purpose
1. Try Catch Error -- catchAsyncError (Done in middleware folder)
2. Error For If conditions -- error (Done in middleware folder)

Seperate Class for error
1. errorHandling (Done in utils folder)


